WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
&lt;h2&gt;Weather&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Jefferson City: frost at dawn (31°F), climbing to 83°F with

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:08.000
full sun. Tacoma: 56°F, partly cloudy, rain tomorrow.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Texts&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Katelyn asking about

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:12.000
bird sightings — you two have been trading all week.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:16.000
Alex sent The Verge's Apple 50th anniversary product ranking at

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000
11 PM Friday.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Iran War Escalation&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Houthis launched their first military operation

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:24.000
in support of Iran — a ballistic missile at Israel.

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:28.000
Debris caused fires at a UAE industrial hub. Drone hit

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:32.000
Kuwait airport radar. The 10-day Hormuz extension is the framework

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:36.000
but the situation is more fragile.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;No Kings Protests&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;3,100+ demonstrations planned

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:40.000
nationwide, organizers expecting millions. Two-thirds of RSVPs from outside major

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:44.000
cities, up 40% from June 2025.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;DHS Shutdown Day 43&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Congress left

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:48.000
for two-week recess without a deal. 61,000 TSA workers have

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:52.000
missed three paychecks.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;AI Replacement Watch&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Warhorse Studios (Kingdom Come Deliverance 2)

00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:56.000
fired their Czech-to-English translator and replaced him with AI. No

00:00:56.000 --> 00:01:00.000
warning. 12K upvotes, 1,500 comments on Reddit.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Apple&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Turns 50 Wednesday. iPhone

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:04.000
Air C1X modem matches Qualcomm on speed, wins on latency.

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:08.000
15+ new products expected this year. No iPhone in Lockdown

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:12.000
Mode has ever been hacked.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;From Your Inbox&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Claude Team: Claude Code

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:16.000
can now keep working while you're away. 404 Media: Earth's

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:20.000
magnetic field creating cosmic ray void. The Atlantic: America sliding

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:24.000
toward illiteracy.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Tacoma&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Cherry blossoms blooming at Wapato Hills — gorgeous photos

00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:24.800
on r/Tacoma.&lt;/p&gt;
